 ceo of reliant pharmaceuticals based in liberty corner new jersey he was also the nonexecutive chairman of pharmaceutical product development inc based in wilmington north carolina from  to  in april  mario was appointed to the board of directors for vivus pharmaceuticals vivus is a biotechnology corporation based out of mountain view california the us food  drug administration recently approved the drugs avanfil  qsymia in april and june  respectively avanfil is used in the treatment of erectile dysfunction and qsymia is indicated for weight loss in obese patients trustee of duke universityedit mario has served as a trustee of duke university from  to  and chaired the duke university health system board of trustees from its inception until  on july   he became a trustee emeritus of duke university in  he was awarded the university medal dukes highest recognition of service to the school marios  years on the duke university board made him the second longest serving trustee in the schools history the longest tenure belongs to mary duke biddle trent semans – great granddaughter of washington duke for whom the school is named awards and honorsedit he has held numerous civic and public health positions including chair of the american lung association and chair of the american foundation for pharmaceutical education mario advises the schools of pharmacy at the university of maryland university of rhode island and rutgers university in december  the rutgers university college of pharmacy was renamed the ernest mario school of pharmacy at rutgers university in  mario was recognized for a lifetime of service to the profession of pharmacy when the american pharmacists association awarded him the remington medal the highest award in professional pharmacy he is the th remington medalist referencesedit  a b c new jersey pharmacist receives profession’s highest honor american pharmacists association press release dated december   accessed may    ratish robert  pharmacy graduate